Begin the race for survival ! Frantic isometric racing game with rock music and explosions ! Motor Rock recreates the spirit of the best racing games of the 90s.

Participate in tournaments deadly intergalactic tremendous driving vehicles , destroying your opponents using the isometric tactical or arcade rear view , and win the cup.

On your way to victory you will find opponents who will not make it easy, each representing the five planets of the tournament, and only vehicles , which can only be overcome by using weapons with great firepower. 8 cars with only 10 armor and equippable weapons upgrades available.

If that 's not enough , you can get a secret weapon and enhancements for special points earned by destroying two opponents followed , pushing opponents off the screen and in many other ways .

Do not like playing by yourself? Join your friend in multiplayer and Cattle tournament together! Or test your skills against other players in multiplayer mode !

For creative players : Now ye may create your own circuits and modify any graphical aspect , musician and game mechanics .
